I upvoted, but I have to note one issue about the science:



Biweekly, SCP-2550 is to be administered specially designed Selective Serotonin Reuptake Inhibitors (SSRIs) designed to alter the brain chemistry of the Phoebastria albatrus to increase serotonin production.
附加记录：    

SSRI medications specifically block the destruction of serotonin, not increase the production-it's in the name. L-tryptophan increases production, and drugs that increase the release of serotonin include dextromethorphan, methadone, and ecstasy. I recommend changing the last word to . I know it is picayune, but it is better science.







